{"tid":1938590,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區(21)","createTime":"2020-03-22T15:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T04:17:33.000Z","uid":125609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5fcd5a7850f58000bceb9d53d765981696d6ffdc","tid":1938590,"uid":125609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"21230e951dc6b987f89333bd0864a1a613539dec","tid":1938590,"uid":125609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遊戲初期常見問題 // 實用online tools<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n＞Android/iOS 「Nintendo Switch Online」app已更新，可以scan QR code，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">連機時可以快速打字傾計</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點先可以經Internet去人地個島？<br />\nＡ：請人來嗰位要去機場（遊戲第二日後解放）開放你個島，同時會俾個代碼你。去人個島嗰位去機楊入代碼就得。如果加左Switch主機好友可以唔駛代碼咁開放俾好友入。需要有Nintendo Switch Online會員。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：生果點種？<br />\nＡ：掘個窿，再掉個生果落去，等幾日就有收成。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：地下有啲金色嘅光？<br />\nＡ：掘開佢會有錢袋，掉返袋錢落去會種到錢樹。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：幾點轉第二日？<br />\nＡ：５am<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點炒蘿蔔／大頭菜？<br />\nＡ：星期日早上入股，平日每日留意價格，啱心水價格時賣去，去朋友島賣都得架。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：用design app整嘅圖案可唔可以分享？<br />\nＡ：開左時裝鋪就可以upload上網分享俾人。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咁多巴絲分享作曲/畫畫QR Code係有咩用架？<br />\nA：遊戲到一定程度可以揀一段仔自製音樂做小島鈴聲，間唔中會起遊戲度聽到首歌。而QR Code scan返來嘅Pattern可以著落衫度，又可以鋪落地度，亦可以用作家俱設計等。<br />\n<br />\nQ：無人島個地型係隨機定固定？<br />\nA：一開始會隨機gen四個俾你揀，遊戲進行到一定階段會解鎖整理地型功能。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一個島可以有幾多個動物村民？<br />\nA：十個。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣跑同靜靜雞行(唔想嚇親昆蟲)？<br />\nＡ：跑 &gt; B，靜靜雞行 &gt; 細力推磨菇，捉昆蟲時持網可以長按A預備。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：鋪左啲畫落地下點del走佢？<br />\nＡ：Y<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點掛自製畫去牆／著畫...?<br />\nＡ：去設計app度揀幅畫。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：唔夠樹枝！<br />\nＡ：搖樹，同一棵樹可以多搖幾次<br />\n<br />\nＱ：石頭/礦石無晒點算？<br />\nＡ：用鏟／斧頭鋤石頭，下面Ｑ＆Ａ有張圖係秘技。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣成棵樹移植去其他地方？<br />\nＡ：食完生果可以成棵樹掘起，再去第度掘個窿種。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點解石頭一劈就爆？<br />\nＡ：你食左生果，特效係會劈爆石頭。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點一機多人玩？<br />\nＡ：首先部Switch要開多幾個profile先，再用嗰啲profile入game做教學。之後隨時用遊戲電話app「召集村民」即可。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：玩到幾時先有______？<br />\nＡ：玩落去咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nＱ：有啲氣球飄下飄下點射落來？<br />\nＡ：用丫叉<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣擴大個背包？<br />\nＡ：用5000miles可去狸貓ATM換「口袋整理技巧」<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點拎丫叉/鏟/杆/梯...？<br />\nＡ：玩耐啲就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲捐野俾狸貓/貓頭鷹，多啲同NPC傾計。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點去「外島」／「下西洋」？<br />\nＡ：去狸貓ATM買機票之後去機場。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：一開始點拎多啲鐵礦石／其他素材？<br />\nＡ：2000哩數可換機票去啲素材豐富嘅島。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點釣魚？<br />\nＡ：瞄準魚頭，咬實左魚竿先拉佢上來。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：有無私人儲物空間？<br />\nＡ：有私樓住之後就有<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點叫醒海邊隻海歐？點揾佢要嘅野？<br />\nＡ：同佢講多幾次野；留意沙地有野識噴水，掘開佢。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：無位擺野！啲野周街放有無問題。<br />\nＡ：擺住出面先；無問題。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：啲屋/設施可唔可以調位？<br />\nＡ：有office後就可以調。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點拎多啲礦石？<br />\nＡ：好似幅圖咁整三個窿先再掘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvjEZrt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvjEZrt.jpg&h=79ad3315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n設計無人島<br />\n<a href=\"https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplanimalcrossing.com%2Fnh%2Fstart%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=8e739228\" target=\"_blank\">https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/</a><br />\n設計無人島國passport 機票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dodoairlines.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dodoairlines.com%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=23099633\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dodoairlines.com/</a><br />\n設計任意pattern, 可生成qr code scan落遊戲度, 可以匯入任意圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://acpatterns.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facpatterns.com%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=4f1e22c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://acpatterns.com/</a><br />\n設計無人島主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://tunes.nooknet.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftunes.nooknet.net%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=7eaefb73\" target=\"_blank\">https://tunes.nooknet.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"72634832096b3d16851009868db055d344f37642","tid":1938590,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JN0trEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJN0trEV.png&h=53e4f26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVrMdjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVrMdjZ.png&h=22eefa27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6117304daa31cea79138f0bc0b224853c02e556","tid":1938590,"uid":126032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9779a19aaa7b4614586ce25f5fbdd5fff948d099","tid":1938590,"uid":131468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有樂器可以幫手訂多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結他 鼓之類"},{"pid":"3ddcbf424c043025e0eae3df4922d3e1faec2afe","tid":1938590,"uid":125609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2abe2aa8dd5b77d72d0367129727268a85a293","tid":1938590,"uid":2146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6117304daa31cea79138f0bc0b224853c02e556","tid":1938590,"uid":126032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"唔放入屋個倉？"},{"pid":"df9231